description: Leigh does a nice interview with Joe Pass - not sure when, probably late 1980's. (If anyone sees this and knows the date please let me know and I'll edit it in).  Joe talks about his life in the music business and the musicians that inspired him early in his career.
title: Joe Pass interview (undated)
